külas mu õde vaatamas...


408
00:43:49.463 --> 00:43:51.338
Hr Kachigunda.
- Pr Sikelo.


409
00:43:52.505 --> 00:43:55.171
Tema on William Kamkwamba -
minu õpilane.


410
00:43:56.005 --> 00:43:57.613
